<form id="encryption_key" method="POST" action="/onboarding/encryption_key">
  <h4>1. Encryption Key</h4>

  <p>
    <code>fastlane.ci</code> uses an encryption key to encrypt your API tokens
    and passwords written out to the private configuration repository generated
    at the end of onboarding.
  </p>

  <ol>
    <li>
      Enter an encryption key we will use to encrypt your password in the
      private configuration repo we will generate:
    </li>
    <div class="mdl-textfield mdl-js-textfield">
      <label for="input"><code>FASTLANE_CI_ENCRYPTION_KEY</code></label>
      <input
          id="encryption_key"
          class="mdl-textfield__input"
          type="text"
          name="encryption_key"
          value="<%= keys[:encryption_key] %>"
          placeholder="Some custom encryption key"
      />
    </div>

    <li>Save your encryption key by submitting the form:</li>
    <input type="submit" value="Save encryption key">
  </ol>
</form>
